      "text": "Umm..\n\nThat's an anti-pattern.\n\nIt's not required.  It's not even recommended.\n\n~~~PowerShell\n$var             # implicit scope\n$local:var    # local scope\n$script:var  # script / module scope\n$global:var # global scope\n~~~\n\nScopes stack, so we can also\n\nGet-Variable -Name var -Scope N"
